</div>
<p>In exploring this data, I was more interested in specific Pokémon’s idiosyncracies rather than overall trends. I began with a simple question in mind: which Pokémon should be my new favorite?</p>
</section>
<section id="finding-blissey" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="finding-blissey">Finding Blissey</h2>
