<p>The above plot shows that Blissey (marked in pink) has the highest health of any Pokémon in the data set. Her close second is her pre-evolved form, Chansey, and all other close competitors are acheived in the late game and are generally more well-rounded than Blissey. Blissey is the unique “tank” Pokémon in the franchise, meaning that her primary purpose to take hits and survive, not to deal damage.</p>
